    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for solid, dependable transportation at an honest price? This fair-condition vehicle is a great option for budget-conscious buyers who need reliable daily transportation! You'll notice some visible wear on the interior and exterior \u2014 think minor scuffs, some fading, and the kind of character that comes from years of real-world use. Mechanically, it's ready to get you where you need to go without the premium price tag of a newer or shinier option. If you're looking for practical value over perfection, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 20000.0,
