      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, no-frills vehicle that gets the job done without breaking the bank? This car is honestly priced for its condition \u2014 it runs and drives, making it a practical choice for everyday errands and commuting! You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections that come with regular use, and there may be a few mechanical items worth addressing down the road. But if you're after reliable basic transportation at a fair price, this one is worth a look \u2014 come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 17000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition at $33,000, and that's an honest, accurate representation of what you'll find. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a decent shine with only minor surface scratches and light scuffs that are typical for a vehicle of this age. There are no significant dents or rust issues to be concerned about. The interior is clean and functional, with normal wear on the seats and surfaces but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts consistently, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in good working order. You may find some minor items that could use attention over time, as is expected with a used vehicle, but nothing that should cause immediate concern. This is a solid, dependable car that has been maintained reasonably well and is ready for daily driving. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a completely honest and accurate representation \u2014 this car is as close to perfect as you will find on the used market. The exterior is genuinely flawless, with no scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind; the paint retains its original deep luster and the body panels are straight and true. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 seats, carpets, headliner, and all trim pieces show zero wear, staining, or damage, presenting as if the car just rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent working order: the engine starts immediately, runs smoothly, and all systems \u2014 brakes, transmission, steering, electronics, and climate control \u2014 function exactly as intended. Tires have substantial tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic work, no surprises. What you see is exactly what you get, and what you get is exceptional.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
