      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly & Full of Potential \u2014 An Honest Deal for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 we're keeping it real with you! It does run, but it needs noticeable work to get back to its best. The exterior shows significant wear including dents, scratches, and paint issues, and the interior reflects its age and use. Mechanically, it requires attention and repairs before it's fully road-ready. This one is ideal for a hands-on buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for an affordable project \u2014 priced accordingly to reflect exactly what you're getting. No surprises, just an honest opportunity! \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f",
